        "Location": "LOCATION_WET_RAT",
        "PublicId": "130495144143",
        "ScenePath": "assembly:/_pro/scenes/missions/wet/scene_rat_basic.entity",
        "TileImage": "$($repository 92532bb0-0f92-4bbe-847f-4c248729cb14).Image",
        "Description": "They have a public name, philanthropic smiles, clean hands, and even cleaner bank accounts.\rThey also have secrets that the public prefers to ignore. People call them &quot;The Three Butchers.&quot; The newspapers talk about disappearances and bought silences. I call it a problem that can be solved cleanly.\r\rI&apos;m not here for revenge. I&apos;m here for the truth. The truth is clean, can be quantified, and can be revealed. We don&apos;t destroy lives to create others—we expose them, we remove power, we confiscate",
